These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-1::.
6 different pets are kept: goldfish, lizard, cat, turtle, goat, ferret
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, van, trike, airplane, car, bike
1. the person driving the boat is the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the owner of the turtle is the person driving the bike##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the car##2
5. the person driving the car is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
8. the owner of the ferret is the person driving the trike##1
9. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |     3      |  4   |     5      |    6    |
| Pet         | goat     | cat | goldfish | turtle | ferret      | lizard |
| Transport   | airplane | car  | boat    | bike | trike | van    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: drama, adventure, family, spy, superhero, thriller
There are 6 different nationalities: american, nigerian, colombian, argentine, canadian, thai
 1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the american##1
 2. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the american##1
 4. the thai is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 5. the person watching family movies is the argentine##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 7. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the canadian is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the canadian##1
10. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |      5      |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama  | spy  | superhero | adventure   | thriller | family |
| Nationality   | colombian | canadian | nigerian    | thai | american   | argentine   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: punk, dubstep, classical, gospel, pop, trance
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: sailing, cricket, climbing, skiing, snowboarding, surfing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
4. the fan of gospel is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
6. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person who's sport is skiing is the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |    3    |       4       |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | punk    | pop | classical     | dubstep         | gospel       | trance     |
| Sport         | sailing | climbing  | cricket | surfing | snowboarding | skiing |

