.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: disaster, fantasy, musical, documentary, time-travel, animation
The people use 6 different means of transport: subway, bike, snowmobile, taxi, jet-ski, helicopter
1. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the snowmobile is the person watching musical movies##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
8. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
9. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | fantasy     | musical     | documentary | time-travel | animation |
| Transport     | helicopter    | bike | snowmobile | taxi  | jet-ski       | subway      |

