.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: fantasy, action, disaster, mystery, horror, thriller
The people use 6 different means of transport: quad-bike, airplane, ship, trike, subway, scooter
 1. the person driving the trike is between the person watching disaster movies and the person driving the ship##2
 2. the person watching action movies is the person driving the scooter##1
 3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 7. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
10. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
11. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
12. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |     4      |     5      |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | mystery | fantasy | thriller    | disaster    | action |
| Transport     | airplane         | quad-bike       | ship  | trike | subway | scooter   |

