 5. the fan of country is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the fan of electronic is in an odd position##4
 7. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the fan of soul is the chinese##1
 9. the fan of country is on the far left or far right##3
10. the nigerian is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

