.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-7::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  police-officer, social-worker, doctor, journalist, designer, videographer
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: rowing, volleyball, golf, ice-hockey, handball, basketball
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is the videographer##1
 2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the journalist##3
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the videographer##1
 6. the designer is on the right of the social-worker##1
 7. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
 8. the doctor is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 9. the police-officer is in an even position##4
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2       |         3          |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Job     | journalist | social-worker     | designer | police-officer  | doctor     | videographer |
| Sport   | volleyball         | handball | ice-hockey              | golf | rowing | basketball |

