.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-8::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, lemonade, soy-milk, almond-milk, fanta
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: fanta-polo, golf, biathlon, sailing, skiing, soccer
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 3. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4
 8. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
10. the person who's sport is fanta-polo is in an odd position##4
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
12. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |    3     |       4       |     5      |      6       |
| Beverage   | coffee | lemonade     | 7up | fanta         | almond-milk        | soy-milk       |
| Sport      | biathlon       | sailing | fanta-polo  | soccer | skiing | golf |

