.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-9::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, lemonade, milk, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
The people have 6 different hobbies: card-games, chess, woodworking, collecting, reading, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
2. the person who's hobby is chess is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person drinking lemonade and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4       |   5    |     6     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | lemonade       | juice     | hot-chocolate     | milk  | soy-milk    |
| Hobby      | collecting | card-games | fishing | woodworking | chess | reading |

