 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 6. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is the person driving the bus##1
10. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
