 4. the person driving the motorbike is between the person driving the car and the person driving the van##2
 5. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 7. the person driving the van is in an even position##4
 8. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 9. the person driving the car is the person eating banana##1
10. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
