.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-20::.
There 6 different types of food: broccoli, kale, cranberry, cauliflower, lemon, grapes
The people have 6 different jobs:  analyst, chef, project-manager, engineer, entrepreneur, software-developer
 1. the engineer is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
 2. the person eating lemon is in an even position##4
 3. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 4. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
 5. the software-developer is on the right of the engineer##1
 6. the person eating broccoli is the entrepreneur##1
 7. the person eating cranberry is in an even position##4
 8. the project-manager is on the far right##1
 9. the analyst is between the person eating lemon and the chef##2
10. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
11. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
12. the engineer is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |   3    |   4    |       5        |     6      |
| Food   | broccoli    | cranberry      | cauliflower  | lemon  | grapes           | kale  |
| Job    | entrepreneur | chef | analyst | engineer | software-developer | project-manager |

 